### Enrichment
FalkorDB released FalkorDBLite in 2026 -- embedded zero-config Python graph database (pip install falkordblite), no Redis needed. Could simplify beestgraph dev/testing. Python client updated Feb 2026, supports 3.10-3.14. Async operations via falkordb.asyncio with connection pooling. FalkorDB positions as best Knowledge Graph for LLM (GraphRAG) using GraphBLAS.

